description: TEHRAN – In a televised interview on Tuesday night, President Ebrahim Raisi boasted the Operation True Promise in retaliation to Israel’s air raid attack on the Iranian consulate in Syria in early April, saying the retaliatory operation proved that “powerful Iran can remove the shadow of war” and also “military option” against the country.

description: Nine US senators have called on the administration of President Joe Biden to consistently apply the Leahy Law to Israel.

description: Hundreds of Israelis staged rallies calling for the cabinet of Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu to agree to the terms of a ceasefire deal that Hamas accepted earlier on Monday, according to the Guardian.

description: Farshad Mehdipour, Deputy Press Secretary of Iran's Ministry of Guidance, led a delegation of Iranian media managers to Iraq, where they met with high-ranking officials from the country. The visit aimed to strengthen bilateral ties and foster cooperation in the media sector between the two nations.

description:
On May 1, 2024, a delegation of Iranian media managers started a four-day visit to Iraq, discussing ways to fortify relations and cultivate collaboration between the two neighboring nations.
The mission was led by Farshad Mehdipour, the deputy for media affairs and publicity in the Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance.
title: Media executives meet Iraqi officials for collaboration talks
